archimate:Contract.name: Power Apps Premium
archimate:Contract.documentation: The Power Apps Premium License is a tiered offering by Microsoft providing advanced capabilities for building and deploying custom applications within its ecosystem. It grants access to premium connectors, on-premises data gateways, and custom API integrations. Users can create an unlimited number of applications or flows, subject to the service limits. Additional features include enhanced server-side logic processing, increased data storage, and extended administrative controls. This license is designed for businesses requiring extensive customization and integration to support complex workflows.
